data.enText: the waste liquid that collects in the bladder and that you pass from your body

example: there was blood in his urine
the child had to make water

value.def: Urine is the liquid that you get rid of from your body when you go to the toilet.

partsOfSpeech.dec: urin 尿 + al 表物 → 尿壶；小便池
urin 尿 + ary …的 → 尿的；泌尿器的
urin 尿 + ate 做，造成，使… → 排尿
ur 尿 + ology …学 → 泌尿学
